Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.schedule

Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.schedule.Schedule
public class Schedule extends Object
This class represents the schedule that the user can use to interact with the Courses. It can create a schedule for the current user and provides functionality for naming the schedule, adding a Course to the schedule, removing a Course from the schedule, getting information of Courses in the schedule, and resetting the schedule.
Author:
Thien Nguyen, Miles Hollifield, Victor Hermida
